title: Zach Sherwin
description: Zach Sherwin (MC Mr Napkins! The Midnight Show pilot! Comedy!) is our very first rapper to come on the show and boy does Pete enjoy dropping his limited hip hop knowledge at his feet for an interesting and hilarious convo between two friends. A rap battle may happen. Or is read, at least. ENJOY YOU WEIRDOS!
